title: U.S. Census, Coastal counties Population, birth, death, immigration data 2000 and 2008, USA, May 2010
name: U.S. Census, Coastal counties Population, birth, death, immigration data 2000 and 2008, USA, May 2010
description: The poly shapefile has decennial population, births, deaths and immigration related data for the 225 coastal counties in the lower 48 states from year 2000 and 2008. The data was released by Census recently just before the start of the 2010 Hurricane season. Find elsewhere on Finder! pop and housing data for coastal counties in the lower 48 states. Also find data on population components (birth, deaths, immigration etc) for all the counties in the lower 48 states and for all the coastal counties. Use key words "Census", "housing", "population" in Finder!
